<DATELINE>HOWICK, Quebec (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   An oil truck crashed into a moving freight
train Monday, killing the truck driver and derailing 15 freight
cars, police and witnesses reported.
   The accident occurred at a crossing 36 miles south of Montreal
